Example 2 : A National Zoopark in India is dealing with the problem of segregation of the animals based on the different attributes they have.
            Build a KNN model to automatically classify the animals. Explain any inferences you draw in the documentation.

Solution :  Business Objective : To classify the animals in Zoo based on their physical appearance & features.

            Constraints :  There can be more features & factors to classify the animals.

Data Dictionary :

Name of the          Description	      Type	             Relevance
feature	                
animal name	      Boolean     	      Non-numeric	    Irrelevant, useful for analysis
hair	            Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
feathers	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
eggs	            Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
milk	            Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
airborne	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
aquatic	          Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
predator	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
toothed	          Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
backbone	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
breathes	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
venomous	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
fins	            Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
legs	          Legs of the animals;
                values - 0,2,4,5,6,8	Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
tail	            Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
domestic	        Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
catsize	          Boolean	            Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
type	          Class of animals;     Numeric	        Relevant, useful for analysis
                integer values in 
                  range 1 - 7


This Repository contains following files :
1. Zoo_KNN.py file
2. Summary of the Repository
3. Dataset : zoo.csv
